Additional Secretary and Financial Adviser to Union Ministry of Steel Bharathi S. Sihag, is the new Chairman-cum-Managing Director of iron ore mining company NMDC Ltd.The Ministry has given her additional charge of the post with effect from January 1, the NMDC said in a regulatory filing on Tuesday. Her appointment is for three months or till appointment of a regular incumbent or until further orders, according to the filing that cited the Ministryâ€™s order of January 11.The previous CMD Narendra Kothari had retired on December 31.